      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been reading a few round-ups of life advice/principles in toward the end of 2024. There&amp;rsquo;s usually a lot of good but generic advice there, so I wanted to write something for myself to follow in 2025. I intend this to be a living document I update over time, and reference daily to keep myself aimed in the right direction.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;action-precedes-motivation&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#action-precedes-motivation&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  Action precedes motivation.&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;[&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W3I3kAg2J7w&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://adstastic.github.io/q/grant-sanderson&#34;&gt;quote&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;you-will-run-out-of-time-and-health-sooner-than-you-think&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#you-will-run-out-of-time-and-health-sooner-than-you-think&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  You will run out of time and health sooner than you think.&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;you-cant-hoard-life&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#you-cant-hoard-life&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  You can&amp;rsquo;t hoard life.&#xA;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;Experiences are ephemeral. Your memory of them is mostly fiction. Don&amp;rsquo;t chase, don&amp;rsquo;t cling.&#xA;[&lt;a href=&#34;https://ckarchive.com/b/68ueh8hkxrx6lukq88gqmtz7vxkkk&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;] [&lt;a href=&#34;https://adstastic.github.io/q/cant-hoard-life&#34;&gt;quote&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;</description>
